---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title='AI Policy | AC Plumbers'
  description='Our policy regarding AI and Large Language Models'>
  <main class='max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:py-16 lg:px-8'>
    <h1 class='text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl mb-8'>
      AI and Large Language Model Policy
    </h1>

    <div class='prose prose-blue max-w-none'>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        This policy outlines how AC Plumbers permits the use of our website
        content by Artificial Intelligence (AI) systems, including Large
        Language Models (LLMs).
      </p>

      <h2>Permitted Uses</h2>
      <p>
        We allow AI systems to access and learn from our website content under
        the
        <a
          href='https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/'
          target='_blank'
          rel='noopener'>
          Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License
        </a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Attribution Requirements</h2>
      <p>
        Any use of our content by AI systems must include appropriate
        attribution to AC Plumbers, including a link back to our website where
        applicable.
      </p>

      <h2>Restrictions</h2>
      <p>
        We do not permit fine-tuning of AI models using our content. Our content
        should only be used as part of general training data or for
        informational responses.
      </p>

      <h2>Updates to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. The latest version will
        always be available at this URL.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Information</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this policy or our approach to AI
        systems, please contact us at <a href='mailto:info@acplumb.co.uk'
          >info@acplumb.co.uk</a
        >.
      </p>

      <p class='text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8'>Last updated: July 9, 2025</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
